<br>
7. Balancing things though expansions. Good idea business wise, bad idea customer wise. Mainly geared at SoL and PoP. People shouldn't have to pay extra money for their class to be fixed, or expect skills and have them be utterly broken for years and yers. *cough* Frenzied Burnout *Cough* Servant of Ro *Cough* .......... Ahem ........<br>
